Inflatable kayaks are also great for paddling enthusiasts that dont want to drive around with a kayak on their rooftop! AIRHEAD travel kayaks fit easily into the trunk of your car, duffel bag or suitcase. So, when you feel the need to paddle, your kayak is with you! The AHTK-5 Airhead Roatan Inflatable 2 Person Kayak is 10 ft. length with 2 seats available. It is designed for lakes and moderate white water, and also provides a lightweight, compact, and portable design. It is constructed of semi-rigid heavy gauge PVC with a tubular I-beam floor for superior comfort, buoyancy, and tracking. The seats are removable and also provide great back support. Two oversized valves are available for quick inflating or deflating, and there is also a drain hole with a plug.Airhead Roatan Inflatable 2 Person Kayak AHTK-5
